<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.9.5">
<l>koḷḷum payaṉillai kuppai kiḷarttaṉṉa celvattai</l>
<l>vaḷḷal pukaḻntunum vāymai yiḻakkum pulavīrkāḷ</l>
<l>koḷḷak kuṟaivilaṉ vēṇṭiṟṟel lāntaruṅ kōtileṉ</l>
<l>vaḷḷal maṇivaṇṇaṉ taṉṉaik kavicolla vammiṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no benefit to take, you poets who lose your truth</l>
<l>in praising the liberality of wealth that shines up in heaps.</l>
<l>Come to say a poem on the one of sapphire colour, my liberal man</l>
<l>without fault who gives all one wants, he who is without want to take.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
